class.name: de.amberhome.preferences.PreferenceManagerWrapper
class.comment: Provides access to the saved settings. Using PreferenceManager you can get the stored values and modify them.

method.name: SetString
method.comment: Maps the given key to the given String value.

method.name: SetList
method.comment: Maps the given key to the given List.

method.name: GetAll
method.comment: Returns a Map with all the Keys and Values. Note that changes to this map will not affect the stored values.

method.name: GetBoolean
method.comment: Returns the Boolean value mapped to the given key. Returns False if the key is not found.

method.name: GetLong
method.comment: Returns the Long value mapped to the given key. Returns -1 if the key is not found.

method.name: SetBoolean
method.comment: Maps the given key to the given Boolean value.

method.name: GetBoolean2
method.comment: Returns the Boolean value mapped to the given key. Returns the default value if the key is not found.

method.name: GetString
method.comment: Returns the String value mapped to the given key. Returns an empty string if the key is not found.

method.name: GetUpdatedKeys
method.comment: Returns a list with the keys that were updated since the last call to GetUpdatedKeys. Note that the updated keys may include keys with unchanged values.

method.name: SetLong
method.comment: Maps the given key to the given Long value.

method.name: GetString2
method.comment: Return the String value mapped to the given key. Returns the default value if the key is not found.

method.name: GetLong2
method.comment: Returns the Long value mapped to the given key. Returns the default value if the key is not found.
